==Finnish==
{{Finnish index|kä}}

===Etymology===
From ''[[käydä]]'' + ''[[-ttää]]''.

===Verb===
'''käyttää'''

#(''transitive'') to [[use]].
#(''transitive'') to make something [[ferment]].
#(''transitive'') (''colloquial'') to take someone somewhere for a [[visit]]; place something for a short duration somewhere.

